        </h2>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px">
          <span style="font:600 17px var(--serif);color:var(--fern-600)">Everyone can make a difference.</span>
          <span style="color:var(--heart)">♥</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font:400 15px/1.7 var(--sans);color:var(--ink-700);max-width:440px;margin:0">Whether you partner with us or stay connected through WhatsApp updates, your involvement helps us sow kindness across Singapore.</p>
      </div>
      <div data-fade class="blob-img-wrap" style="position:relative;width:130%;transform:translateX(-80px);aspect-ratio:1431/928;-webkit-mask-image:url(/illustrations/section-8-blob-mask.svg);mask-image:url(/illustrations/section-8-blob-mask.svg);-webkit-mask-size:100% 100%;mask-size:100% 100%;-webkit-mask-repeat:no-repeat;mask-repeat:no-repeat">
